Happy TOT everyone! I survived going to the vet yesterday! Here is an update. At my age, I have to go a lot. But that’s ok, he takes very good care of me. As of now, I get a shot every 4 weeks to help keep an infection I have in my teeth/gums from spreading. He doesn’t want to pull any teeth due to my age and all. I also have to have ear drops cause as you all know, us pugs tend to get ear infections easily. Then to top it off, my eyes need drops due to the little vessels in my eyes that are spreading towards my cornea and causing me to see squiggly lines. The drops will help to get them to go away so I can see better. But this is the life of a senior. And I’m ok with that. I can still be as feisty as ever, especially when snackies are involved!
